    "title": "Quad Word",
    "pageid": 2011,
    "redirects": [],
    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Programming\" title=\"Programming\">Programming</a> * <a href=\"/Data\" title=\"Data\">Data</a> * Quad Word</b>\n</p><p>According to <a href=\"/Intel\" title=\"Intel\">Intel's</a> definition of a <a href=\"/X86\" title=\"X86\">x86</a> 16-bit <a href=\"/Word\" title=\"Word\">Word</a>, a <b>Quad Word</b> refers a 64-bit word.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#long_long_or_long\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">long long or long</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Bitboards\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Bitboards</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Ranges\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Ranges</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Alignment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Alignment</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Endianness\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Endianness</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Litte-endian_Layout\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Litte-endian Layout</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Big-endian_Layout\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Big-endian Layout</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"long_long_or_long\">long long or long</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quad_Word&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: long long or long\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Microsoft 64-bit <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a>-compiler long is still 32-bit <a href=\"/Double_Word\" title=\"Double Word\">Double Word</a>, while 64-bit <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GCC\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GCC</a> uses 64-bit Quad Words as longs. Other compiler require \"long long\" for 64-bit types.\n</p>\n<pre>\ntypedef unsigned long QWORD;\ntypedef unsigned long long QWORD;\n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bitboards\">Bitboards</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quad_Word&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Bitboards\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Quad words are used as <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboard</a> datatype:\n</p>\n<pre>\ntypedef QWORD U64;\ntypedef QWORD Bitboard;\n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ranges\">Ranges</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quad_Word&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Ranges\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n\n<tr>\n<th> language\n</th>\n<th> type\n</th>\n<th> min\n</th>\n<th> max\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"2\"> <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a>, <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a>\n</td>\n<td>  unsigned long long\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 18,446,744,073,709,551,615\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  hexadecimal\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0x0000000000000000\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0xFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"2\"> <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a>, <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a>,<br /><a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a>\n</td>\n<td>  long long\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> -9,223,372,036,854,775,808\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 9,223,372,036,854,775,807\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  hexadecimal\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0x8000000000000000\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0x7FFFFFFFFFFFFFFF\n</td></tr></table>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Alignment\">Alignment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quad_Word&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Alignment\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Quad Words stored in memory should be stored at byte addresses divisible by eight. Otherwise at runtime it will cause a miss-alignment exception on some processors, or a huge penalty on others.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Endianness\">Endianness</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quad_Word&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Endianness\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><i>Main article: <a href=\"/Endianness\" title=\"Endianness\">Endianness</a>.</i>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Litte-endian_Layout\">Litte-endian Layout</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quad_Word&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Litte-endian Layout\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/Little-endian\" title=\"Little-endian\">little-endian</a> memory layout, as typical for <a href=\"/Intel\" title=\"Intel\">Intel</a> cpus.\nFor instance the quad word integer 0x0102030405060708\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n\n<tr>\n<th> Address\n</th>\n<th> Byte\n</th>\n<th> Significance\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0000\n</td>\n<td>  0x08\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"> LS Byte\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0001\n</td>\n<td>  0x07\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0002\n</td>\n<td>  0x06\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0003\n</td>\n<td>  0x05\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0004\n</td>\n<td>  0x04\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0005\n</td>\n<td>  0x03\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0006\n</td>\n<td>  0x02\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0008\n</td>\n<td>  0x01\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"> MS Byte\n</td></tr></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Big-endian_Layout\">Big-endian Layout</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quad_Word&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Big-endian Layout\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/Big-endian\" title=\"Big-endian\">big-endian</a> memory layout, as typical for <a href=\"/index.php?title=Motorola&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Motorola (page does not exist)\">Motorola</a> cpus.\nFor instance the quad word integer 0x0102030405060708\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n\n<tr>\n<th> Address\n</th>\n<th> Byte\n</th>\n<th> Significance\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0000\n</td>\n<td>  0x01\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"> MS Byte\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0001\n</td>\n<td>  0x02\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0002\n</td>\n<td>  0x03\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0003\n</td>\n<td>  0x04\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0004\n</td>\n<td>  0x05\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0005\n</td>\n<td>  0x06\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0006\n</td>\n<td>  0x07\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  0x0007\n</td>\n<td>  0x08\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"> LS Byte\n</td></tr></table>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quad_Word&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Byte\" title=\"Byte\">Byte</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Word\" title=\"Word\">Word</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Double_Word\" title=\"Double Word\">Double Word</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">Bitboards</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quad_Word&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Word_%28computer_science%29#Dword.2C_Qword.2C_and_Oword\">Dword, Qword, and Oword from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Byte\">Byte from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Endianness\">Endianness from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://betterexplained.com/articles/understanding-big-and-little-endian-byte-order/\">Understanding Big and Little Endian Byte Order</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ietf.org/rfc/ien/ien137.txt\">IEN 137 - DAV's Endian FAQ - On Holy Wars and a Plea for Peace</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.myri.com/staff/cohen/\">Danny Cohen</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ai.isi.edu/\">U S C/I S I</a>, April 1, 1980</li></ul>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Data\" title=\"Data\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301065217\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.006 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.007 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 53/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 80/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:2011-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301065217 and revision id 2747\n -->\n"
